description: The research of ragweed , the food of the gods that can give superhuman powers , is the focus of this summer adventure . The hunt for the secret recipe involves - in addition to Martin , Diana and Java - a gang of criminals , Altrove , Angie and the demented duo & Dee Kelly . Guest of honor: the brilliant private detective Milo Thorpe , a man of culture and intelligence matched only by its physical grandeur !
name: Il cibo degli Dei

description: The columns of the Mezquita of Cordoba hide a passage to an unknown dimension that , in 1926 , was visited by the brilliant Dutch engraver M. C. Escher , who was influenced by it throughout his life . These days , a friend of Angie is trapped in the same dimension and Mystere investigates his disappearance . But the path of Martin crosses , with unpredictable outcomes , with those of the gangster boss Don Manzanera.
name: Il mondo di Escher
